(ijQy mwieAw dy moh dy kwrn sihm hY auQy Awqmk AwnMd nhIN plHr skdw, pr) jy koeI mnu`K gurU vloN mUMh moV ley (aus nUM Awqmk AwnMd nsIb nhIN ho skdw ikauNik) gurU qoN ibnw mwieAw dy pRBwv qoN ^lwsI nhIN imldI[
byS`k iksy ivcwrvwnW qoN jw ky pu`C lvo (qy qs`lI kr lvo, ieh p`kI g`l hY ik gurU qoN ibnw) iksy BI hor QW qoN mwiek bMDnW qoN ^lwsI nhIN imldI[
(mwieAw dy moh ivc PisAw mnu`K) AnykW jUnIAW ivc Btkdw AwauNdw hY, gurU dI srn qoN ibnw ies moh qoN ^lwsI nhIN imldI[
Aw^r gurU dI crnIN l`g ky hI mwieAw dy moh qoN Cutkwrw imldw hY ikauNik gurU (shI jIvn-mwrg dw) aupdyS suxWdw hY[
nwnk AwKdw hY ik ivcwr ky vyK lvo, gurU qoN ibnw mwieAw dy bMDn qoN AwzwdI nhIN imldI, (qy ies mukqI qoN ibnw Awqmk AwnMd dI pRwpqI nhIN ho skdI) ]22]
